Configs/GameConfig/Test/Data/

# =============================================================================
# 保留项说明（默认会提交）
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# - KayanoClient/Assets/GameScripts/     热更与主程代码
# - KayanoClient/Assets/TEngine/         框架与 Editor
# - KayanoClient/Assets/AssetRaw/UI/     UI Prefab（不含 UIRaw 贴图）
# - KayanoClient/Assets/AssetRaw/Configs/*.csv / *.asset  配置与本地化
# - KayanoClient/Assets/Scenes/          场景
# - KayanoClient/Packages/manifest.json  包依赖
# - KayanoClient/ProjectSettings/
# - Configs/GameConfig/luban.conf、Defines、CustomTemplate、转表脚本
# - KayanoServer/Hotfix、Entity 源码
# =============================================================================
